name: r-bs4dash
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-bs4dash
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/bs4Dash_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/bs4Dash/bs4Dash_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1dd07a730ed19c64d1ff6fdf0f37336a0bc2358684811ccde95973c81b4c85cf

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-bslib >=0.2.4
    - r-fresh
    - r-htmltools >=0.5.1.1
    - r-httpuv >=1.5.2
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.16
    - r-lifecycle
    - r-shiny >=1.6.0
    - r-waiter >=0.2.3
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-bslib >=0.2.4
    - r-fresh
    - r-htmltools >=0.5.1.1
    - r-httpuv >=1.5.2
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.16
    - r-lifecycle
    - r-shiny >=1.6.0
    - r-waiter >=0.2.3

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('bs4Dash')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('bs4Dash')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://rinterface.github.io/bs4Dash/index.html, https://github.com/RinteRface/bs4Dash
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Make 'Bootstrap 4' dashboards. Use the full power of 'AdminLTE3', a dashboard template built on top of 'Bootstrap 4'  <https://github.com/almasaeed2010/AdminLTE/tree/v3-dev>.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
